64
00:03:25,590 --> 00:03:26,510
Keep your voice down.

65
00:03:28,790 --> 00:03:29,829
No guts.

66
00:03:30,110 --> 00:03:31,430
Don't you know Xu Ao?

67
00:03:31,710 --> 00:03:33,310
According to Socrates,

68
00:03:33,950 --> 00:03:37,670
