grow into your best self.]

188
00:08:46,270 --> 00:08:47,110
Hey,

189
00:08:47,860 --> 00:08:49,350
thanks for today.

190
00:08:51,030 --> 00:08:51,910
As long as you're happy.

191
00:08:54,230 --> 00:08:56,110
